Rhea Ripley in my opinion is the wrestler of the year!!!! Look at what she did this year: Became first NXT UK women's champion
Won the first ever Women's Wargames down 4 to 2
Pinned Sasha Banks to win the Survivor Series for NXT
Best both Sasha and Charlotte Flair on consecutive nights on Raw and Smackdown
And now won the NXT Women's Championship over the 2-time Champion Shayna Baszler.
Tell me who had a better year than Ripley? No one!!!! And she just turned 23 years old. Phenomenal!!!!
